                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 9.094,
                                "byte_start": 90846,
                                "byte_stop": 127313,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in No. 90-6861, Mccarthy against Madigan will be announced by Justice Blackmun."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 9.094,
                        "stop": 122.07,
